name: JapanTimes(FlashBriefing)
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Latest news and features from Japan: business, politics, commentary culture, life & style, entertainment and sports.

Receive daily updates from Japan Times in your Flash Briefing. This app is simply a reader of the Japan Time's public rss feed intended for users daily Flash Briefings. 

The developer of this skill is in no way officially affiliated with "Japan Times" and has no plans of monetization, or anything other than the Flash Briefing operation of "Japan Time's" public rss feed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
